"replace_text": _charToReplace = " " _newChar = "" _newStr = "" ! intialize a new empty string _i = 1000 ! creating a "guard" for the while, set the max number of runs while _currStr <> "" and _i > 0 do _n = STRSTR (_currStr, _charToReplace, 1) ! check the script for _charToReplace if _n > 0 then ! _charToReplace is first found in position _n
! add the first part of _currStr to _newStr, plus add _newChar _newStr = _newStr + STRSUB (_currStr, 1, _n - 1) + _newChar
! get a new _currStr from the chars after position _n _currStr = STRSUB (_currStr, _n + 1, STRLEN(_currStr) - _n) else ! if _charToReplace is not found then add _currStr to _newStr _newStr = _newStr + _currStr ! close the loop with changing _currStr to empty string _currStr = "" endif _i = _i - 1 ! decrease the "guard" variable in each run endwhile return
